    <title>Syria contributor: Rim El Gantri</title>
    <description>Rim El Gantri is an expert on human rights and transitional justice. Previously the International Center for Transitional Justice’s head of office in Nepal and Tunisia, she has experience in public administration, election management and law. She also worked at the International Foundation for Electoral Systems on initiatives to ensure fairness and transparency in Tunisia’s first democratic elections.
</description>
